#Email Onebox Backend API Tests
###
GET http://localhost:3000/

### get emails by page limit
GET http://localhost:3000/emails?page=1&limit=10

### Get all emails
GET http://localhost:3000/emails

### Get email by search query
GET http://localhost:3000/emails/search?q=interview

### Get email by account
GET http://localhost:3000/emails/account/yourgmail@gmail.com